member.summary:
Defines options to control Cross-Origin Resource Sharing (CORS) for an
index.  (see https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/azure/dn798941.aspx
for more information)

Defines a function that boosts scores based on the value of a date-time
field.  (see https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/azure/dn798928.aspx
for more information)

Optional. Gets or sets a value indicating whether to apply a
constant boost for field values beyond the range end value;
default is false.
